data.title: Auburn Hills Michigan ZIP Codes - Map and Full List
data.meta_description: List and Interactive Map of All ZIP Codes in Auburn Hills Michigan
data.text:
Auburn Hills Michigan is covered by a total of 2 ZIP Codes. There are also 1 ZIP Codes that overlap Auburn Hills but have a different postal city name. The ZIP Codes in Auburn Hills range from 48309 to 48326. Of the ZIP codes within or partially within Auburn Hills there are 1 Standard ZIP Codes and 1 PO Box ZIP Codes. The total population of ZIP Codes in Auburn Hills is 24105.

Click on the ZIP Codes in the interactive map to view more information. The map control in the upper right corner can be used to toggle map layers on and off. The red outline is the border of Auburn Hills and can be turned on and off. Each type of postal code can also be turned on and off.
